
== Howto activate SSL on trytond ==

- You need to have OpenSSL and pyOpenSSL installed on your system.

- Generate a self-signed certificate with this command:

    openssl req -new -x509 -keyout server.pem -out server.pem -days 365 -nodes

- Start the trytond server with those options:

    trytond.py -S --privatekey server.pem --certificate server.pem
